<br>
I asked a friend about this and he told me that he had encountered this before and that it was a bug where the golems still had held agro to the corpses.  The solution to this was to have everyone with a corpse up there to camp out for 15 minutes to clear the agro of the golems.  Alas, not everyone did this so the problem was not fixed.  <br>
<br>
This is the reason why CR was so difficult because three times we had clerics at the camp to rez and every time they got agroed.  Mainly from sitting down and increasing the agro radius.<br>
<br>
So this isnt something Verant has changed in the plan.  It was merely a bug that made CR a pain in the ass.<br>
<br>
Thanks goes out to PC for helping us clear these pesky mobs and rezzing the corpses.  Thanks a bunch guys = )<br>
